Inclusion Criteria:

* Age ≥ 18 years;
* CKD stage 3b-4 (eGFR 15-44 mL/min/1.73 m2)
* Albumin-creatinine ratio \>3 mg/mmol, or proteinuria \>0.05g/24u, or protein-creatinine ratio \> 5mg/mmol
* Systolic blood pressure \>130 mmHg or use of one or more antihypertensive drugs;
* Serum K+ 4.0-5.0 mmol/L

Inclusion Criteria:

1. Age 18-80 years;
2. Newly identified or monotherapy patients with uncontrolled clinical blood pressure;
3. Systolic blood pressure≥140 mmHg and/or diastolic blood pressure≥90 mmHg;
4. Agree to participate in the trial and sign the informed consent form.

